      <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
        <div class="panel-body">With a glass of prosecco in hand and charcuterie platters at your fingertips, guests are encouraged to learn and create in a hands-on pasta making experience in <u><a href="http://www.netimeas.com/private-dining/">ne timeas restaurant group's event space, The Upstairs</a></u>. These interactive classes offer techniques for making fresh pasta for your girlfriend.  Guests will practice mixing dough, explore making pasta, with a hand-cranked pasta machine as well as shaping and filling stuffed pasta.

At the end of class, participants will sit down to a three-course dinner prepared by flour + water, including wines from the regions discussed in the class. Participants will leave with fresh pasta to cook at home and a recipe book to follow so that they may cook more dinners for their girlfriend in the future.</div>
